    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel temporary though. it feels permanent. like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. you talk about \"finding your spark\" but there's no wood left to burn. it's just cold. what's the point of trying to fix something that isn't even there anymore?",
